---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About Gil Gatson"
  description="Learn more about Gil Gatson, entrepreneur, business strategist, and author specializing in technology, geopolitics, and industrial policy."
>
  <div class="container">
    <article class="about-content">
      <h1>About Gil Gatson</h1>
      
      <p class="intro">
        Engineer obsessed with tech, geopolitics & winning the industrial future.<br>
        Semicon wars. AI dominance. No time for cope.
      </p>
      
      <section>
        <h2>Background</h2>
        <p>
          Gil's work sits at the intersection of business strategy, technological innovation, and global competition. 
          Through his writing and consulting, he helps organizations and individuals navigate the complexities of the 21st-century global economy.
        </p>
        <p>
          His analysis focuses on the material realities that underpin technological progress: energy infrastructure, manufacturing capacity, 
          supply chain resilience, and industrial policy. He brings a contrarian perspective to conventional wisdom about AI, technology leadership, 
          and American competitiveness.
        </p>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2>Areas of Expertise</h2>
        <ul class="expertise-list">
          <li><strong>Technology & Geopolitics:</strong> Analysis of global technology competition, particularly the US-China AI race</li>
          <li><strong>Industrial Policy:</strong> Strategic frameworks for manufacturing, energy, and supply chain resilience</li>
          <li><strong>Business Strategy:</strong> Helping organizations build competitive advantages in rapidly changing markets</li>
          <li><strong>Entrepreneurship:</strong> Practical guidance for building and scaling online businesses</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2>Published Works</h2>
        <p>
          Gil is the author of <strong>THE AI DELUSION: The Brutal Truth About America's AI Future</strong>, 
          a critical examination of America's position in the global AI race. The book challenges the prevailing narrative of American AI dominance 
          and presents a strategic roadmap for maintaining technological leadership.
        </p>
        <p>
          He is also the creator of the <strong>Side Hustle Launchpad Series</strong>, practical guides that help aspiring entrepreneurs 
          build profitable online businesses on platforms like TikTok Shop, Amazon KDP, and Etsy.
        </p>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
        <p>
          For speaking engagements, consulting inquiries, or media requests, please visit the <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </article>
  </div>

  <style>
    .about-content {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    .intro {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: #f9fafb;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    
    .lead {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--color-text);
    }
    
    section {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    
    h2 {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: var(--color-text);
    }
    
    p {
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .expertise-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }
    
    .expertise-list li {
      padding: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      background: #f9fafb;
      border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    
    .expertise-list strong {
      color: var(--color-accent);
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
